  m_sTextData "I. Situation"\
  ""\
  "a. Enemy forces"\
  ""\
  "One American mechanized infantry company to the north west, seemingly preparing for a push in our direction."\
  "One platoon was observed establishing a screen 1.5km away from our current location. Aerial reconnaissance spotted another platoon staging for a possible movement, while a third one has seemingly remained in reserve for now."\
  ""\
  "b. Friendly Forces"\
  ""\
  "Reconnaissance platoon (SPW-40P2), currently near Allenburg. One vehicle has established an OP ahead of Wasserberg."\
  "Company of Motor Rifle troops (SPW-70), its platoons have established defensive positions at Wasserberg, Allenburg and Kasselberg. Its tank platoons T-72s are in firing positions further back."\
  "Mortar element at Kasselberg, ready to respond in case the reconnaissance platoon locates an enemy force."\
  "Battalion level support elements further south east near Sonnenberg, preparing for withdrawal while the company defends/delays."
