  m_sTextData "II. Mission"\
  ""\
  "Assault and secure either Wasserberg or Allenburg, then Kasselberg."\
  ""\
  "III. Execution"\
  ""\
  "The purpose of this operation is to clear a path towards Sonnenberg for 3rd platoon, either on the north east by securing Wasserberg or on the south west by securing Allenburg."\
